column5: So I entered a contest after the fishing show for a Rapla Army slash bait and to my surprise I won one of the lures in the give away. Hers a pic.  I never win jack so wnated to share. I dont know if these are a limited run or not, but thought it was cool.
looks like it was designed for the wild rogue camoflaged pike
Now how are the fish gonna see that lure  Congrats on the win.  Go buy a lottery ticket now
Hahahaha my thoughts exactly Joey lol. Any boat contests ??lol
Nice look! You gonna keep it or sell it?

SirWhite I think I'll just keep it sealed in the box and hang onto it. I honestly have enough blue,perch,pink and many other colours to play with. I thought when I filled out the contest it said limited number so ill just hold onto it and maybe sell it to Chum Lee in thirty years lol.
Another lure too pretty to throw!
Got mine in the mail yesterday
Sorry .. maybe its just me ... but I couldnt see it ...
